│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ The fix is to apply `bit_floor` to the result of the division, just like it's done in line 3815.                                                                                         │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ The line to change is 3819.                                                                                                                                                              │
│ Original: `std::min(MaxSafeElementsPowerOf2, SLDist / WidestType);`                                                                                                                      │
│ Fixed: `std::min(MaxSafeElementsPowerOf2, bit_floor(SLDist / WidestType));`                                                                                                              │
